text: Car park everywhere crack. Home stay unit having same issue, lift not working as usual, even the bomb shelter staircase wall are cracking. Previous comment remove for "some reason".

Very nice layout. Many condos today are no longer as nice and generous as this. Plenty of space for swimming, walkways are wide and easy to move things around. Will definitely extend my contract here next time
Fantastic condo. Recent TOP, been looking at many condos to buy and this one is unique as they are generous with the space. Wide walkways and decent communal furnishings. Got quality.
Well-managed with organized operations, friendly staff, and a relaxing place to stay.
